<p>Can anyone be more clueless? Just last week, Michael Sheehan, the assistant secretary of defense for special operations told the Senate Armed Services committee that the "war on terror" will last "<a href="http://www.wired.com/dangerroom/2013/05/decades-of-war/">At least another 10 to 20 years</a>."<br /></p>
